fulltitle: Legendary Jazz Bassist Ron Carter on Discipline and Practicing
description: In this clip from www.artistshousemusic.org - Jazz legend Ron Carter discusses what hes learned from classical music  for example discipline and practice techniques that allowed him when he was younger to maximize his technical and musical prowess.
title: Legendary Jazz Bassist Ron Carter on Discipline and Practicing
